# Project Structure Guide

This is a Next.js 15 project with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and StackFrame integration.

## Key Files and Directories

- **Entry Point**: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with StackFrame provider
- **Main Page**: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Home page component
- **Stack Configuration**: [src/stack.tsx](mdc:src/stack.tsx) - StackFrame server app setup
- **UI Components**: [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/) - Radix UI components with shadcn/ui styling
- **Utilities**: [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) - Common utility functions including `cn()` for class merging
- **Hooks**: [src/hooks/](mdc:src/hooks/) - Custom React hooks
- **Configuration**: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with path aliases
- **Dependencies**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Path Aliases
- `@/*` maps to `./src/*` (configured in tsconfig.json)

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript with strict mode
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Radix UI components
- StackFrame for error tracking
- React Hook Form with Zod validation
